Class Employee

  • java.lang.Object
    • driver.Employee
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable

    public class Employee
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    Employee object which stores and allows access to the first name, last name, gender, tenure, rate and salary.\ Implements the comparable interface allowing for the last name to be compared.
